                    Indian cuisine. Our goal at Just Eat It is to unify our guest's culture and
                    spirits with our own, expressing passion and cuisine we share. 
                </p>

                <p>Whether part of a party of fifty or a part of two, yout experience 
                    throughout our elegant, yet comfortable space is eventful. We are sharing our
                    long held Indian traditions with a modern contemporary twist. You will feel
                    both close to home and apart of something new.  
                </p>
                <div class="image-container">
                    <img src="images/about-thumb-01.jpg">
                    <img src="images/about-thumb-02.jpg">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="video-content">
                <img src="images/about-video-bg.jpg">
            </div>
        </article>
    </section>

